description:
Rookie Hannah “The Black Swan” White thought she was a real tough guy after winning her first match in the Summer Vengeance Tournament.

She quickly realizes when going up against Penny “The Tarrasque” Play, that trying to beat someone ranked #8 is a whole lot harder than beating someone ranked #16…
title: Summer Vengeance Tournament: 15 vs 8 - Rookie Learns the Hard Way
